How to create a .deb file

Execute ./createDeb.sh to make a new games-in-pygames.deb file.

You can install games-in-pygames.deb by executing
 dpkg -i games-in-pygames.deb

Afres that two new files must be places in /usr/local/games
asteroides.py is the python code of the asteroides games
asteroides is a shell script that executes python /usr/local/games/asteroides.py

Play asteroides by writing asteroides in the shell
user@host:~$asteroides
